100 Balls
=============
Open source clone of 100 Balls for Ubuntu for Phones

Based on Bacon2D, a framework to ease 2D game development, providing
ready-to-use QML components useful for creating compeling games.

Installation
-------

First, you need Bacon2D on your system:
https://github.com/Bacon2D/Bacon2D

After you clone this repository, you can launch the game with qmlscene:
qmlscene 100balls.qml

Contribution
-------
If you want to help with developement, or you have a suggestion, write to
riccardo AT rpadovani DOT com or ping rpadovani on #ubuntu-app-devel on
Freenode :-)
